<topic id="forcing_page_breaks">
    <title>Forcing Page Breaks</title>
    <body>
        <p>To always move the content at the beginning of the page, let say before the title of a section, you can use: </p>
        <codeblock outputclass="language-css">section h1 {
    page-break-before: always;
}</codeblock>
        <p>Or, if you want to have only a specific element on a single page:</p>
        <codeblock outputclass="language-css">div.notice {
    page-break-before: always;
    page-break-after: always;
}</codeblock>
    </body>
</topic>
